            "title": "Contrasting patterns of elevational zonation for birds and mammals in the Andes of southeastern Peru",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Bruce D.",
                    "lastName": "Patterson"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
